        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T06n0220_399:1068b03_33",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來法身即是諸法真如、法界，真如、法界既不可說有來有去，如來法身亦復如是無來無去。",
        "from": "T06n0220_399:1068b03_34",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『復次，善男子！",
